rows.label: tlk44500184_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I never would have imagined
things would come to this...

rows.label: tlk44500184_03_msg0002
rows.name:
But still, I believe in you.
I'm with you all the way.

rows.label: tlk44500184_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Ever since you passed through these
gates, I get the sense that the country's
finally got up off its backside.

rows.label: tlk44500184_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Ah, I don't mean in a bad way. What's
good for Alst's good for Luxuria. You
just keep fighting for the greater good!
